original_title: Matt Okine: Being Black n Chicken n Shit
overview: Award-winning comedian Matt Okine is black and likes chicken... but he's also chicken of some seafood. During what was supposed to be a routine fishing trip with his dad, Matt comes face-to-face with ghost fishermen, killer jellyfish, and giant squid, tackling his gravest fears, all in the hope of getting a little breakfast.
title: Matt Okine: Being Black n Chicken n Shit
